4chan Ergonomics
A new simplistic meme hot off the internet presses. <s>Whether or not</s> '''it's a [[forced meme]]'' <s>is presently a topic of [[Boring|intense debate.]]</s>

It has caused its creators to spend almost [[over 9000| as many hours]] in MS Paint as [[MSPaint Relationship Thread]]s and [[RAGE|FFFFFFUUUUUU]] threads combined.

The set up follows as thus: <br>
Hey, /[[b]]/.
<br>
How do you sit at your [[computer]]?
<br>
[[Pic related]]: it's how I'm sitting at my computer right now.
{{clear}}
[[Image:Ergonomics60.jpg|frame|left]]
'''GENIUS'''

{{clear}}
